Package rats

Interface Summary
Animal Represents all animals that can be put into a maze.
 

Class Summary
FarSeeingRat Type of Rat <\ br> This Rat type determines which way to go at intersections it does not have a clear decision of by examining the Maze ahead and seeing which is the longest route it can take.
Maze Represents a sewer maze through which rats can run.
MemoryRat Type of Rat that uses previous moves to determine where to move next
RandomRat Type of Rat that only ever moves randomly
Rat This is the abstract class Rat which can be used to move around a Maze
